ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: It's about the history of the photographic book in which you read various books that summarize a photographic movement as photography evolves throughout the ages. You get to utilize the vast resources of the Beneicke. And your semester project is on whatever interests you in photography.I would recommend the class.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: It allowed me a better understanding of the evolution of photography and the photographer's role in photography. It did not contribute to my personal research but helped fulfill a graduation requirement.
